&lt;h3&gt;The Mission&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Eubrics is an AI-native platform purpose-built for financial-services firms. Our product trains financial advisors, insurance agents, wealth managers, and retail-banking professionals to deliver higher-impact client conversations — measurably improving advice quality and conversion rates. With meaningful traction in India and a growing portfolio of enterprise clients — including Kaiser Permanente, Farmers Insurance, and Accenture — across banking, insurance, and wealth, we are now building our North America go-to-market engine from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
