&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring a &lt;strong&gt;Founding Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt; – the first dedicated seller at Kana. You&#39;ll work directly with the CRO and the founders to take a thoughtful, founder-led sales motion and turn it into a repeatable one. This is a build role, not a plug-and-play role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In your first six months, you&#39;ll:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
