&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GTM Engineer (AI-First)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Kana&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kana is the agentic marketing platform built for the AI era. Founded by the team behind Rapt (acquired by Microsoft) and Krux (acquired by Salesforce for $700M), Kana emerged from stealth in February 2026 with $15M in seed funding led by Mayfield.&lt;/p&gt;
