&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scale High-Volume Outreach:&lt;/strong&gt; Deploy, test, and manage outbound email sequences via &lt;strong&gt;Instantly.ai&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;Valley&lt;/strong&gt; for signal-based LinkedIn outreach to ensure high deliverability and AI-driven personalization at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the System of Record:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain &lt;strong&gt;HubSpot&lt;/strong&gt; as the single source of truth. Build the automated &quot;plumbing&quot; that moves leads from discovery to booked meetings with zero manual data entry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Inbound &amp;amp; SEO Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Leverage &lt;strong&gt;SEMRush&lt;/strong&gt; to identify high-intent keywords and gaps then use AI platforms to generate and deploy high-converting content across our marketing channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paid Search and Social Management and Optimization: &lt;/strong&gt;You’ll manage paid search and paid social campaigns and ensure that all message testing, positioning and experimentation is being fed directly into our paid channels to optimize outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optimize &amp;amp; Iterate:&lt;/strong&gt; Treat the funnel like code. You will constantly A/B test messaging, landing pages, and workflows, using data to kill what isn&#39;t working and double down on what is.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Master the Kana Platform:&lt;/strong&gt; Acting as &quot;Customer Zero&quot; for Kana’s agentic platform, you will, in parallel, deploy our internal AI agents to find audiences, optimize digital campaigns, and ensure our brand is discoverable in the LLM ecosystem

