&lt;h3&gt;About super{set}&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;super{set} is a venture studio that conceives, funds, and builds companies from formation through scale. We don’t just write checks — we co-found companies and stay deeply involved at the strategy, positioning, and operational layers. Our portfolio spans AI-native software, fintech, and developer tooling.&lt;/p&gt;
